        <p><a href="/translations">Compare the best Odyssey translations</a> — Emily Wilson, Fagles, Lattimore side by side — or browse <a href="/gift-guide">recommended editions and gifts</a> for the serious reader.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout> 
